<!-- XTRA PR71 launcher icon - Option D "Device Mark" monochrome layer.
     Single-colour silhouette for Android 13+ themed icons: the launcher ignores
     colour and tints the whole drawable by its alpha, so everything is solid white
     and the decorative diagonal accent is dropped to keep the mark clean.
     Placement (translate 18 / scale 0.6 into the 72dp safe zone) matches the
     foreground layer so the themed icon lines up with the full-colour one. -->
